<div id="review_2239790073" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2239790073" />
    <a title="Kathleen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39134508-kathleen"><img alt="Kathleen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1495314753p2/39134508.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2239790073?book_show_action=true">Jan 14, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathleen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathleen" href="/user/show/39134508-kathleen">Kathleen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780062065209" href="/book/show/9592214-faith">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/39134508-kathleen?shelf=read-in-2018">read-in-2018</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/39134508-kathleen?shelf=group-author-of-the-month">group-author-of-the-month</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/39134508-kathleen?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2239790073" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9941718475943730608">4.5 stars<br/>Since joining this Goodreads book club, I have been introduced to some great books and several of my &apos;now&apos; favourite authors. Jennifer Haigh was January author of the month in our reading group, and although I had never heard her name before, I did not hesitate to search my local library, where I located the book FAITH copyright in 2011. <br/><br/>Sheila McGann narrates the story of her older brother, Arthur Breen, who once was a beloved Catholic priest of suburban Boston. He is the favourite of </span>
  <span id="freeText9941718475943730608" style="display:none">4.5 stars<br />Since joining this Goodreads book club, I have been introduced to some great books and several of my 'now' favourite authors. Jennifer Haigh was January author of the month in our reading group, and although I had never heard her name before, I did not hesitate to search my local library, where I located the book FAITH copyright in 2011. <br /><br />Sheila McGann narrates the story of her older brother, Arthur Breen, who once was a beloved Catholic priest of suburban Boston. He is the favourite of Mary, the devout Catholic mother of three children. When he is accused of inappropriate behaviour with a young boy, Shelia takes time off teaching and flies home. Mike believes the rumours and shuns his brother, while Sheila, believing in his innocence, searches for the truth. <br /><br />I was fully engaged in this suspenseful story of secrets, family and loyalty, doubt and belief. The 2004 movie The Good Shepherd (not to be confused with a later movie of the same name) has some aspects of plot that are similar. <br /><br />Jennifer Haigh is a talented author and I look forward to reading more of her books. </span>
  <a data-text-id="9941718475943730608" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


